{
  "video_id": "h9deGh8_tEc",
  "title": "The boost students need to overcome obstacles | Anindya Kundu",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12917.0,
      "end_time": 17737.0,
      "text": "So, I teach college students about inequality and race in education,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 17761.0,
      "end_time": 20826.0,
      "text": "and I like to leave my office open to any of my students"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 20850.0,
      "end_time": 23381.0,
      "text": "who might just want to see me to chat."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 23405.0,
      "end_time": 24952.0,
      "text": "And a few semesters ago,"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 24976.0,
      "end_time": 27881.0,
      "text": "one of my more cheerful students, Mahari,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 27905.0,
      "end_time": 29302.0,
      "text": "actually came to see me"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 29326.0,
      "end_time": 33977.0,
      "text": "and mentioned that he was feeling a bit like an outcast because he's black."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 34100.0,
      "end_time": 36873.0,
      "text": "He had just transferred to NYU from a community college"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 36898.0,
      "end_time": 38660.0,
      "text": "on a merit scholarship,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 38684.0,
      "end_time": 40518.0,
      "text": "and turns out,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 40542.0,
      "end_time": 43824.0,
      "text": "only about five percent of students at NYU are black."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 43848.0,
      "end_time": 45277.0,
      "text": "And so I started to remember"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 45301.0,
      "end_time": 47830.0,
      "text": "that I know that feeling of being an outsider"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 47854.0,
      "end_time": 49534.0,
      "text": "in your own community."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 49558.0,
      "end_time": 51777.0,
      "text": "It's partially what drew me to my work."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 51801.0,
      "end_time": 53320.0,
      "text": "At my university,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 53560.0,
      "end_time": 55452.0,
      "text": "I'm one of the few faculty members of color,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 55477.0,
      "end_time": 59302.0,
      "text": "and growing up, I experienced my family's social mobility,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 59326.0,
      "end_time": 62549.0,
      "text": "moving out of apartments into a nice house,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 62573.0,
      "end_time": 64928.0,
      "text": "but in an overwhelmingly white neighborhood."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 65293.00000000001,
      "end_time": 66443.0,
      "text": "I was 12,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 66467.0,
      "end_time": 70419.0,
      "text": "and kids would say that were surprised that I didn't smell like curry."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 70443.0,
      "end_time": 71666.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 71690.0,
      "end_time": 73634.0,
      "text": "That's because school is in the morning,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 73659.0,
      "end_time": 75531.0,
      "text": "and I had Eggo waffles for breakfast."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 75555.0,
      "end_time": 76705.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 77184.0,
      "end_time": 78413.0,
      "text": "Curry is for dinner."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 78437.0,
      "end_time": 79887.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 80412.0,
      "end_time": 81793.0,
      "text": "So when Mahari was leaving,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 81817.0,
      "end_time": 84809.0,
      "text": "I asked him how he was coping with feeling isolated."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 84833.0,
      "end_time": 87580.0,
      "text": "And he said that despite feeling lonely,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 87820.0,
      "end_time": 89157.0,
      "text": "he just threw himself at his work,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 89182.0,
      "end_time": 91635.0,
      "text": "that he built strategies around his grit"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 91659.0,
      "end_time": 93566.0,
      "text": "and his desire to be successful."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 93945.0,
      "end_time": 96850.0,
      "text": "A mentor of mine is actually Dr. Angela Duckworth,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 96874.0,
      "end_time": 101741.0,
      "text": "the psychologist at UPenn who has defined this stick-to-activeness of grit"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 101765.0,
      "end_time": 105445.0,
      "text": "as being \"the perseverance and passion for long-term goals.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 105469.0,
      "end_time": 107646.0,
      "text": "Angela's book has become a bestseller,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 107670.0,
      "end_time": 109681.0,
      "text": "and schools across the country,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 109705.0,
      "end_time": 111420.0,
      "text": "particularly charter schools,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 111444.0,
      "end_time": 114911.0,
      "text": "have become interested in citing \"grit\" as a core value."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 115320.0,
      "end_time": 117306.0,
      "text": "But sometimes grit isn't enough,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 117330.0,
      "end_time": 119230.0,
      "text": "especially in education."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 119254.0,
      "end_time": 121122.0,
      "text": "So when Mahari was leaving my office,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 121146.0,
      "end_time": 123824.0,
      "text": "I worried that he might need something more specific"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 123848.0,
      "end_time": 126164.0,
      "text": "to combat the challenges that he mentioned to me."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 126760.0,
      "end_time": 130290.0,
      "text": "As a sociologist, I also study achievement,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 130530.0,
      "end_time": 132232.0,
      "text": "but from a slightly different perspective."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 132256.0,
      "end_time": 135429.0,
      "text": "I research students who have overcome immense obstacles"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 135453.0,
      "end_time": 137770.0,
      "text": "related to their background."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 137101.0,
      "end_time": 138733.0,
      "text": "Students from low-income,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 138757.0,
      "end_time": 140794.0,
      "text": "often single-parent households,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 140818.0,
      "end_time": 145655.0,
      "text": "students who have been homeless, incarcerated or perhaps undocumented,"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 145679.0,
      "end_time": 148108.0,
      "text": "or some who have struggled with substance abuse"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 148132.0,
      "end_time": 150624.0,
      "text": "or lived through violent or sexual trauma."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 151319.0,
      "end_time": 154327.0,
      "text": "So let me tell you about two of the grittiest people I've met."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 155770.0,
      "end_time": 157751.0,
      "text": "Tyrique was raised by a single mother,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 157775.0,
      "end_time": 160629.0,
      "text": "and then after high school, he fell in with the wrong crowd."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 160653.0,
      "end_time": 162545.0,
      "text": "He got arrested for armed robbery."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 162569.0,
      "end_time": 165270.0,
      "text": "But in prison, he started to work hard."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 165510.0,
      "end_time": 166876.0,
      "text": "He took college credit courses,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 166901.0,
      "end_time": 169547.0,
      "text": "so when he got out, he was able to get a master's,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 169571.0,
      "end_time": 171929.0,
      "text": "and today he's a manager at a nonprofit."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 172782.0,
      "end_time": 175462.0,
      "text": "Vanessa had to move around a lot as a kid,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 175486.0,
      "end_time": 178852.0,
      "text": "from the Lower East Side to Staten Island to the Bronx."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 178877.0,
      "end_time": 181848.0,
      "text": "She was raised primarily by her extended family,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 181872.0,
      "end_time": 184342.0,
      "text": "because her own mother had a heroin addiction."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 184812.0,
      "end_time": 185962.0,
      "text": "Yet at 15,"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 185986.0,
      "end_time": 187606.0,
      "text": "Vanessa had to drop out of school,"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 187630.0,
      "end_time": 189130.0,
      "text": "and she had a son of her own."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 189313.0,
      "end_time": 192803.0,
      "text": "But eventually, she was able to go to community college,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 192827.0,
      "end_time": 194322.0,
      "text": "get her associate's,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 194346.0,
      "end_time": 197598.0,
      "text": "then go to an elite college to finish her bachelor's."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 198261.0,
      "end_time": 200785.0,
      "text": "So some people might hear these stories and say,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 200809.0,
      "end_time": 202817.0,
      "text": "\"Yes, those two definitely have grit."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 202842.0,
      "end_time": 205706.0,
      "text": "They basically pulled themselves up by the bootstraps.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 206500.0,
      "end_time": 208488.0,
      "text": "But that's an incomplete picture,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 208512.0,
      "end_time": 210330.0,
      "text": "because what's more important"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 210570.0,
      "end_time": 214158.0,
      "text": "is that they had factors in their lives that helped to influence their agency,"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 214182.0,
      "end_time": 215857.0,
      "text": "or their specific capacity"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 215882.0,
      "end_time": 219446.0,
      "text": "to actually overcome the obstacles that they were facing"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 219470.0,
      "end_time": 222841.0,
      "text": "and navigate the system given their circumstances."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 223176.0,
      "end_time": 224652.0,
      "text": "So, allow me to elaborate."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 224965.0,
      "end_time": 228298.0,
      "text": "In prison, Tyrique was actually aimless at first,"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 228322.0,
      "end_time": 230381.0,
      "text": "as a 22-year-old on Rikers Island."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 230917.0,
      "end_time": 234219.0,
      "text": "This is until an older detainee took him aside"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 234243.0,
      "end_time": 236784.0,
      "text": "and asked him to help with the youth program."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 236808.0,
      "end_time": 238251.0,
      "text": "And in mentoring youth,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 238275.0,
      "end_time": 241861.0,
      "text": "he started to see his own mistakes and possibilities in the teens."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 242365.0,
      "end_time": 245939.0,
      "text": "This is what got him interested in taking college-credit courses."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 245963.0,
      "end_time": 247143.0,
      "text": "And when he got out,"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 247167.0,
      "end_time": 249381.0,
      "text": "he got a job with Fortune Society,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 249405.0,
      "end_time": 253105.0,
      "text": "where many executives are people who have been formerly incarcerated."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 253543.0,
      "end_time": 256209.0,
      "text": "So then he was able to get a master's in social work,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 256233.0,
      "end_time": 260668.0,
      "text": "and today, he even lectures at Columbia about prison reform."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 261570.0,
      "end_time": 262549.0,
      "text": "And Vanessa ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 262573.0,
      "end_time": 264637.0,
      "text": "well, after the birth of her son,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 264661.0,
      "end_time": 267941.0,
      "text": "she happened to find a program called Vocational Foundation"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 267965.0,
      "end_time": 269981.0,
      "text": "that gave her 20 dollars biweekly,"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 270500.0,
      "end_time": 271163.0,
      "text": "a MetroCard"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 271187.0,
      "end_time": 273373.0,
      "text": "and her first experiences with a computer."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 273397.0,
      "end_time": 276741.0,
      "text": "These simple resources are what helped her get her GED,"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 276765.0,
      "end_time": 279620.0,
      "text": "but then she suffered from a very serious kidney failure,"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 279644.0,
      "end_time": 283708.0,
      "text": "which was particularly problematic because she was only born with one kidney."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 283732.0,
      "end_time": 287858.0,
      "text": "She spent 10 years on dialysis waiting for a successful transplant."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 288423.0,
      "end_time": 289728.0,
      "text": "After that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 289752.0,
      "end_time": 292574.0,
      "text": "her mentors at community college had kept in touch with her,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 292598.0,
      "end_time": 294235.0,
      "text": "and so she was able to go,"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 294259.0,
      "end_time": 296358.0,
      "text": "and they put her in an honors program."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 296382.0,
      "end_time": 299123.0,
      "text": "And that's the pathway that allowed her to become accepted"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 299147.0,
      "end_time": 302486.0,
      "text": "to one of the most elite colleges for women in the country,"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 302510.0,
      "end_time": 304986.0,
      "text": "and she received her bachelor's at 36,"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 305110.0,
      "end_time": 307787.0,
      "text": "setting an incredible example for her young son."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 308782.0,
      "end_time": 312971.0,
      "text": "What these stories primarily indicate is that teaching is social"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 312995.0,
      "end_time": 315360.0,
      "text": "and benefits from social scaffolding."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 315384.0,
      "end_time": 318194.0,
      "text": "There were factors pushing these two in one direction,"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 318218.0,
      "end_time": 321670.0,
      "text": "but through tailored mentorship and opportunities,"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 321910.0,
      "end_time": 323615.0,
      "text": "they were able to reflect on their circumstances"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 323639.0,
      "end_time": 326151.0,
      "text": "and resist negative influences."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 326175.0,
      "end_time": 329685.0,
      "text": "They also learned simple skills like developing a network,"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 329709.0,
      "end_time": 331350.0,
      "text": "or asking for help --"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 331374.0,
      "end_time": 336178.0,
      "text": "things many of us in this room can forget that we have needed from time to time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 336202.0,
      "end_time": 337699.0,
      "text": "or can take for granted."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 338251.0,
      "end_time": 340820.0,
      "text": "And when we think of people like this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 340107.0,
      "end_time": 344282.0,
      "text": "we should only think of them as exceptional, but not as exceptions."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 344652.0,
      "end_time": 347477.0,
      "text": "Thinking of them as exceptions absolves us"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 347501.0,
      "end_time": 351924.0,
      "text": "of the collective responsibility to help students in similar situations."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 352274.0,
      "end_time": 355878.0,
      "text": "When Presidents Bush, Obama and now even Trump,"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 355902.0,
      "end_time": 359599.0,
      "text": "have called education \"the civil rights issue of our time,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 359624.0,
      "end_time": 361354.0,
      "text": "perhaps we should treat it that way."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 362119.0,
      "end_time": 365831.0,
      "text": "If schools were able to think about the agency that their students have"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 365855.0,
      "end_time": 368348.0,
      "text": "and bring to the table when they push them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 368372.0,
      "end_time": 371371.0,
      "text": "what students learn can become more relevant to their lives,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 371395.0,
      "end_time": 375966.0,
      "text": "and then they can tap into those internal reservoirs of grit and character."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 377900.0,
      "end_time": 378628.0,
      "text": "So this here --"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 378653.0,
      "end_time": 380368.0,
      "text": "My student Mahari"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 380392.0,
      "end_time": 383617.0,
      "text": "got accepted to law school with scholarships,"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 383641.0,
      "end_time": 385157.0,
      "text": "and not to brag,"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 385181.0,
      "end_time": 387704.0,
      "text": "but I did write one of his letters of recommendation."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 387728.0,
      "end_time": 389316.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 389340.0,
      "end_time": 393298.0,
      "text": "And even though I know hard work is what got him this achievement,"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 393322.0,
      "end_time": 395429.0,
      "text": "I've seen him find his voice along the way,"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 395453.0,
      "end_time": 399294.0,
      "text": "which as someone who's grown up a little bit shy and awkward,"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 399318.0,
      "end_time": 401631.0,
      "text": "I know it takes time and support."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 401655.0,
      "end_time": 404789.0,
      "text": "So even though he will rely a lot on his grit"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 404814.0,
      "end_time": 407989.0,
      "text": "to get him through that first-year law school grind,"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 408130.0,
      "end_time": 410417.0,
      "text": "I'll be there as a mentor for him,"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 410442.0,
      "end_time": 412474.0,
      "text": "check in with him from time to time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 412498.0,
      "end_time": 414482.0,
      "text": "maybe take him out to get some curry ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 414506.0,
